verbose_text: In addition, IMT negatively correlated with serum PON1 levels and cellular cholesterol efflux in the peritoneal macrophages and hepatocytes (r = -0.675, P = 0.002; r = -0.69, P = 0.002; r = -0.816, P < 0.001; respectively) and positively correlated with serum MPO activity (r = 0.774, P < 0.001) (data not shown).
